    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see. so you're saying the school is coming from a place of science/psychology while the parents are mostly just coming from a place of religion or ideology? that feels a bit lopsided. aren't there parents who are worried about it for developmental or even just practical reasons, not just because of their religion? it feels like you're framing one side as \"factual\" and the other as just \"opinion.\"",
